import React from 'react'

function Form() {
  return (
    <form className='form'>
        <label >Name</label>
        <input type='text'/>
        <label >Surname</label>
        <input type='text'/>
        <label >Email</label>
        <input type='mail'/>
        <label >Message</label>
        <input type='text' name='message'/>
    </form>
  )
}

export default Form
